SUMMARY:Calling All Halloween Hooligans! Build a Haunted Halloween House!
DESCRIPTION:Spooky season is here! Engage your mind by blending art and engineering to construct your very own haunted house to keep. We’ll be using sturdy milk cartons\, icing as our construction glue\, and sweet and savory treats and candies. All materials provided\, while they last. Dress for a mess! \nThis program is for children between the ages of 8 and 17 years old. Children under the age of 12 MUST be accompanied by an adult. This is a STEAM (Science\, Technology\, Engineering\, Art and Math) Program.
URL:https://marylandstemfestival.org/event/calling-all-halloween-hooligans-build-a-haunted-halloween-house/
LOCATION:Olney Library\, 3500 Olney Laytonsville Rd\, Olney\, MD\, 20832\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts,Engineering,Food
END:VEVENT
