SUMMARY:St. Mary's STEAM Festival
DESCRIPTION:St. Mary’s County Public Schools will host their 10th annual STEAM Festival on Saturday\, October 25\, 2025 at the St. Mary’s County Fairgrounds. Festivities will run from 10:00 am to 2:00 pm and will feature fun\, food\, and phenomena! \nEach year\, the state designates a month-long celebration of all things science\, technology\, engineering\, and math. This STEM-related exploration takes place through in person festivals and online events. Our annual STEAM Festival is set up in a fair-style manner\, where attendees can engage with exhibitors at their own pace.
URL:https://marylandstemfestival.org/event/st-marys-steam-festival/
LOCATION:St Mary’s  County Fairgrounds\, 42455 Fairgrounds Rd\, Leonardtown\, MD\, 20650\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts,Engineering,Physics,Science and Society,Technology
ORGANIZER;CN="St. Mary's County Public Schools":MAILTO:jwhayes@smcps.org
END:VEVENT
